In [76]:
alt.data_transformers.disable_max_rows()
alt.Chart(data).transform_window(
    index='count()'
).transform_fold(
    ['minDate','maxDate']
).mark_line().encode(
     x=('key:N'),
     y=('value:Q'),
    color=alt.Color('timePeriodsKeys:N',title="Time Periods"),
    detail='index:N',
    opacity=alt.value(0.5)
).properties(width=500,
            title="Emergence of periods in Modern Era").interactive()
